Revision history for Perl module Clarion

2007-11-01	1.02	Stas Ukolov <ukoloff@cpan.org>
 * Version number changed

2007-10-24	1.1.2	Stas Ukolov <ukoloff@cpan.org>
 * Correct processing of 'GROUP' fields
 + Memo fields can be padded with ' ' or \0
 * Changed "decryption" algorithm to work on perl 5.6

2007-06-14	1.1.1	Stas Ukolov <ukoloff@cpan.org>
 + Reads memo fields (can be disabled)
 * Correct processing of "encrypted" files
 + Current record can be omited in calls to get_record

2003-11-19	1.01	Ilya Chelpanov <ilya@macro.ru>
 + encrypted files support
 * some bugs fixed

2000-05-11	1.00	Ilya Chelpanov <ilya@macro.ru>
 + first version
